Uses of DynamicAction in net.objectzoo.events.impl
 

Subinterfaces of DynamicAction in net.objectzoo.events.impl
 interface DynamicEventAsyncDelegate
          An DynamicEventAsyncDelegate implements DynamicActionAsync as well as DynamicEventDelegate and is meant as a specification for implementations that delegate calls to the DynamicActionAsync interface asynchronously to all subscribers of the DynamicEventDelegate interface.
 interface DynamicEventDelegate
          An DynamicEventDelegate implements DynamicAction as well as DynamicEvent and is meant as a specification for implementations that delegate calls to the DynamicAction interface to all subscribers of the DynamicEvent interface.
 

Classes in net.objectzoo.events.impl that implement DynamicAction
 class DynamicEventAsyncAdapter
          The DynamicEventAsyncAdapter is class that adapts an DynamicEventDelegate to DynamicEventAsyncDelegate so that the original delegates subscribers can be invoked asynchronously.
 class DynamicEventCaller
          The DynamicEventCaller is a DynamicEventDelegate implementation that allows event distribution to a single subscriber.
 class DynamicEventDistributor
          The DynamicEventDistributor is a DynamicEventDelegate implementation that allows event distribution to multiple subscribers.
